<template>

<el-container>
  <el-aside width="200px">Aside</el-aside>
  <el-main>
    <el-image
      style="width: 100%; height: 100%"
      :src="imageUrl"
      :fit="fit"></el-image>
  </el-main>
</el-container>

</template>

<script>
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      imageUrl: 'require(@../assets/image/background.jpg',
      fit: 'fill'
    };
  },
  // created() {
  //   this.imageUrl = require('../assets/image/background.jpg');
  // }
}
</script>
